{"tid":1495191,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[請置頂重視] 關於律政司想DQ年輕正義律師","createTime":"2019-08-22T03:17:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T01:43:56.000Z","uid":206224,"like":127,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"0d43d51ec9e283062d3bde6b9a70b0bfab37d467","tid":1495191,"uid":206224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:17:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/21/185516_a72dcc63d3526507eb3b28d9813be53c.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F21%2F185516_a72dcc63d3526507eb3b28d9813be53c.jpeg&h=cb5502aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事關今個星期六，律政司好大可能會反對一位有正義感嘅年輕人成為執業律師<br />\n<br />\n另外根據謠傳(未fact check):<br />\n－律師會都收到同一個投訴人嘅投訴，由於律師會出名奶共，所以律師會都有可能聯合律政司DQ事主<br />\n - 事主係做見習律師期間，被佢藍絲老闆篤灰，呢位老闆係做律師之前曾經做過警察<br />\n<br />\n為左支持正義嘅下一代繼續發聲，在此我強烈呼籲連登仔幫幫手：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 一直推post，切勿令呢件事石沉大海<br />\n2. 如果有人識事主，請話比佢知，有好多人願意今個星期六出席佢嘅admission，以和平旁聽形式去聲援佢</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果你係見到呢個post嘅事主，請你勇敢企出黎，我地會全力支持你！</span>"},{"pid":"09702c4d41ee1625ca1eb7eb5e1c409209af872a","tid":1495191,"uid":60219,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:18:15.000Z","msg":"星期六高等法院一日遊"},{"pid":"8dfbc6e93f1291a6f1cdc552c92fadf8245f0a3e","tid":1495191,"uid":206224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:18:47.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"132e244d686b018cb23ee09e868c6025b54b86df","tid":1495191,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:19:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"10f0743ce32a9f57dfe5e38d3e25b72b71bccd98","tid":1495191,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:19:03.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n香港人可攻可守，智勇雙全！<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span